25/04/2011
BELGRADE, Serbia - Christians across the region celebrated Easter on Sunday (April 24th) with festive services. 
Orthodox and Catholic believers gathered in churches and monasteries to mark the biggest Christian holiday. 
Political leaders delivered messages to the public calling for peace and harmony. 
(RTS, ANA-MPA, B92, Balkan Web, VoA, Top Channel - 24/04/11)
